憑空污人清白&hellip;&hellip;」 「什麼清白？我前天解焊9代的蓋, 裏面又是牙膏的。」INTEL 10代的功耗達到224W，身上的風扇咆哮着，爭辯道，「唧牙膏不能算落後&hellip;&hellip;牙膏！&hellip;&hellip;INTEL的事，能算唧麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「單核性能無敵」，什麼「高頻」之類，引得眾RYZEN都鬨笑起來，店內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"7026661c5721433f371b0ca630e30a1cf59d900e","tid":1969011,"uid":131744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3be4374eeeb45d0387fa8f773967bb17f9e7eb7","tid":1969011,"uid":305612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"564ab826f861de95c5618e497b7d9df7d72ada5b","tid":1969011,"uid":131744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c451579e3dbbdc1f84792dc8282f84cf2671db7d","tid":1969011,"uid":131744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T14:50:27.000Z","msg":"佢會解答你 如果佢受保就叫佢寄返新加坡 你當係Back Up Plan"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T14:51:05.000Z","msg":"叫你寄粒U返新加坡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:25:29.000Z","msg":"寄咗之後係咪要幾個月先攞得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T12:33:44.000Z","msg":"2星期拎得返"},{"pid":"1ee0a322dde6b6ed7dbf459b9b380b06b5c56e01","tid":1969011,"uid":37107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64ef11990282afb1623a4cfcc7ce567b4554acbd","tid":1969011,"uid":305612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T06:32:47.000Z","msg":"小弟4月7號買咗先AMD Ryzen 5 3600<br />\n過咗三日之後送咗過嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就諗住自己裝,點知唔知係咪撞跌左個 針腳斷咗 請問依種情況可唔可以攞去保養或者換<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋個星級計劃係咩嚟嘅<br />\n唔該師兄們解答多謝🙏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T08:34:07.000Z","msg":"係邊度買"}]}